data.description: Great location with an oversized lot. This wonderful home has Hardwood floors, an updated kitchen with newer appliances and tile floors, updated windows, and a newer roof in 2018. Enjoy the 3 bedroom plus office and 2.1 baths. Enjoy Year-round use with your covered patio, You have a fully fenced yard, garden area, and large storage shed. A new hot water heater was in 2019, and all new fenced in 2019, two new sliding glass doors in 2023.
